 the role, you would have: Bachelor Degree in Engineering, Computer Science/Information Technology or its equivalent with technical security certifications will be a plus. Expert knowledge of the ISO 27000 series of information security standards and other related industry best-practice standards. Minimum of 15 years of experience in Information security preferably in Banking and Financial services sector, ideally in a in a geographically dispersed team, with a minimum of 5+ years hands-on experience on Policy Development or Communications. Proven experience in managing Policy and Communication Services (e.g. User Awareness Training, Internal Marketing and Communications, Policy Management).About this companyTyche SearchTyche Search is a Singapore firm that was established in 2009. We operate internationally from offices based in Singapore and India and provide recruitment and associated services for executive positions primarily in the Asian Market. To illustrate our position in the market, our search division provide clients with sophisticated candidate sourcing strategies to access the “inactive candidate market” that volume based recruiters don’t have, but deliver with a speed and pricing structure that the traditional search firms don’t match. Our client portfolio includes Global Investment & Retail Banks.Similar jobsSingaporePosted 20 days agoSingaporePosted 11 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoSingaporePosted 20 days agoSingaporePosted 12 days agoSingaporePosted 25 days agoSingaporePosted 28 days agoOrange County…Posted 18 days agoGreater Chicago AreaPosted 5 days agoGreater Boston AreaPosted 8 days agoThis is a preview of the INFORMATION SECURITY - POLICY AND AWARENESS HEAD job at Tyche Search. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 28 days agoSingaporePosted 28 days agoSingaporePosted 2